{"tid":2388960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果啲sales宜家真係幾串下","createTime":"2021-01-31T13:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:22:30.000Z","uid":157152,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"aed03c8b434107078f6176f4762dc04a4e3c540b","tid":2388960,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"事源我係IFC到試緊佢最新個耳機，話啲聲幾靚，我同女朋友講好聲過我屋企個遊戲耳機，個sales就串貢貢問我咩牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話係ROG，跟住佢就話垃圾黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我問，咁你推薦買邊種呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁當然佢就話：買呢個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我試完唔覺有其他連接方法咪問佢個耳機係咪得藍芽連接，佢話係丫<br />\n<br />\n咁我咪話有啲可惜，我部主機板無所以用唔到。<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢好驚訝好串咁講話無可能架喎，主機板點會無藍芽，咁樣點連接野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢仲串我話廿年前既HP機都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟唔熟電腦，所以想問下係咪宜家所有底板都標配藍芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？咁樣比佢串一串我搞到有啲嬲其實，我係入黎想了解下跟住消費，佢就當我弱智咁句句都疾一下先安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：試錶帶個時個姐姐好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fc53781078d52110c3db24c76c9f0009704aa7","tid":2388960,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"1eb6d658a8bec87b65c98a45fc1f624f1ec0d7e0","tid":2388960,"uid":20379,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔知你做乜嘢"},{"pid":"7d80499c961f1351397d7730de1b10dd78ac69f0","tid":2388960,"uid":222581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"589ec771851fb5ce6a77dd8273ad335d0decfbef","tid":2388960,"uid":157152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eb6d658a8bec87b65c98a45fc1f624f1ec0d7e0","tid":2388960,"uid":20379,"like